data.description: Seller says SELL! Stick built solid 2 bedroom 1 bath fixer-upper. Great location, close to town and the beach. Fenced back yard, small deck and a nice little attached garage with washer, dryer and concrete floor. With some TLC this can be a great beach retreat, or your starter home. Fresh paint inside come take a look and make this your beach cabin.
